  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Warsmith Honsou's hatred of Uriel Ventris drives him to attempt the nigh-impossible: capture one of the most heavily defended star forts in the Ultramarines' holdings, an installation that conceals a secret deep at its core. The novella runs the assault strictly from the Iron Warriors' side, Honsou's hand-picked warband against interlocking fortress firepower, and tilts the saga's gravity decisively to chaos-POV. The Ventris obsession is by this point a sustained way of life rather than a phase, and the novella is its rawest articulation. A fast siege-piece carved from a long grudge.",
